    "The rear dormer window would, by reason of its excessive width, scale, mass and siting, not be contained well within the roof space and appear dominant, unduly bulky and visually intrusive in the rear garden environment harmful to the amenity of adjacent occupiers contrary to the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document and Policies 7 and 26 of the Havering Local Plan.",
